    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine currently struggles to stay running and requires significant mechanical attention, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is, and I recommend towing it from the lot.",
