      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be roadworthy. The engine has a severe oil leak and the transmission is currently slipping, making the car unreliable for daily use. Externally, there is noticeable rust on the wheel arches and several deep scratches, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear, including cracked dashboard plastic and stained upholstery. This is a project car for someone with the tools and time to perform a complete overhaul.",
